Spain to Join EU’s Central Platform for CO2 Auctions in 2013

-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a
-- 
2011-02-18T11:09:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/spain-to-join-europe-union-s-central-platform-for-carbon-auctions-in-2013.html
  Spain  will join the European Union’s
common platform for auctioning carbon dioxide allowances when
the third phase of the emissions-trading program begins in 2013,
according to a spokeswoman in the ministry of climate.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ewa Krukowska in Brussels at 
 ekrukowska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
